data.description: Experience the epitome of sustainable luxury living in this exquisite property! Boasting 3 Bedrooms (guest room and full bath on main level) 3 full baths and a generous size office, which could be a home school room. Plus Flexible spaces ideal for a Media room, workout room or even a 4th bedroom. This home seamlessly combines versatility and comfort! Sit on your screened porch or on the upper deck and watch the sunrise or sunset, or sit by your wood burning fireplace with wood cut from your land! 100% solar powered home (paid in full) with reliable back up from Entergy electric & a whole house generator fueled by a 1000 gallon propane tank, you will NEVER BE WITHOUT POWER! Nestled on a ridge w/9.84 acres in Pulaski County this haven offers tranquility while only 18 min to Costco & the shops & dining at the Promenade. Embrace the perfect blend of nature & modern living at its BEST!
